{"tid":1612864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「激憤怒」我屋企個菲傭個朋友對琴日開槍有野講","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:39:17.000Z","uid":326052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d917b90b0bbd851f9f7aefdc22342d48e9706ff3","tid":1612864,"uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"一瞓醒 我屋企個菲律賓工人都話 Hong Kong Police is crazy ！！<br />\n<br />\n佢話佢post咗 警察開槍 擊中個暴徒段新聞喺facebook， 佢菲律賓所有啲朋友都話香港警察有冇搞錯。<br />\n<br />\n佢話喺菲律賓如果啲人咁樣打警察，警察開咗一槍，見對方未死應該向佢開多兩槍 點會仲去救佢㗎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎緊我唔會再佢續約，亦都唔會請菲傭</span></span><br />\n以後紅日係街見到佢地知點做，義士唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a05fcf4ba326dea3fcac8a8ac57e6e3b88974b33","tid":1612864,"uid":262545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"樓主小心啲<br />\n佢咁陰毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efaf9b336c59ba3a9db2bdfa26ec2b76cd7529b","tid":1612864,"uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a92f9ff70ec4c535c1745511452e214b065bcb9","tid":1612864,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"請印傭"},{"pid":"4833c76cdb932da174944f00234c2495ee9cb2d5","tid":1612864,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:39:17.000Z","msg":"識人有個菲傭第一件事係問個朋友 點解你地香港人仲忍到?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}